135
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:27,260
Luckily, Yan came to tutor Le at home.

136
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,580
She even cooked for him.

137
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:31,700
Please don't be so formal with me.

138
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:33,780
Le is smart and well-behaved.

139
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:35,700
Besides, Rui and I are good friends.

140
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:36,940
If you're

141
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,140
too busy,

142
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:39,060
