232
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:59,060
"Chengdu Love Story".

233
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:13,260
Thanks, Yuan.

234
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:14,940
I haven't felt

235
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:16,660
