246
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,620
Thank you.

247
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,300
Get some rest.

248
00:13:41,700 --> 00:13:42,220
I'll head off now.

249
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:42,500
Bye.

250
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:42,980
Bye.

251
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,020
Mom,

252
00:13:57,380 --> 00:13:58,460
